## рҹ”Ң **BACKEND FEATURES (How It Works)**

### **1. WebSocket Connection**

```
Browser вҶҗвҶ’ Flask Backend
В  В вҶ“
Uses Socket.IO library
В  В вҶ“
Persistent two-way communication
В  В вҶ“
Can handle multiple clients
В  В вҶ“
