```

**Connection Info:**
- Address: http://localhost:5000 (or your server)
- Protocol: WebSocket with fallback to HTTP polling
- Auto-reconnect: Yes (every 1-5 seconds)
- Ping timeout: 60 seconds

### **2. Event Handling**

**Server listens for:**
```
вң“ connect - new user joins
вң“ disconnect - user leaves
вң“ join_room - user enters room
вң“ leave_room - user exits room
вң“ send_message - user sends chat message
вң“ typing - user is typing
вң“ private_message - direct message (ready)
вң“ get_online_users - request user list
```

**Server broadcasts:**
```
вң“ message - new chat message
вң“ user_join - someone entered
вң“ user_leave - someone left
вң“ message_history - previous messages
вң“ users_list - current online users
вң“ typing - show typing indicator
вң“ notification - system messages
вң“ error - error occurred
```

### **3. Database Operations**

